sequenceDiagram
    participant V as Vendor
    participant SYS as System
    participant LB as Logistics Bridge
    participant R as Rider (Phone)
    participant C as Customer
    participant GW as WhatsApp Gateway
    participant WA as WhatsApp

    Note over V,SYS: Vendor generates invoice → PROCESSING

    V->>SYS: PATCH order → PROCESSING
    SYS->>LB: POST /api/dispatch-delivery
    LB->>LB: Find first available rider
    LB->>GW: POST /api/send-rider-assignment
    GW->>WA: Rider: New order pickup from [Vendor]. Accept: /rider/orders/[id]/accept?token=...
    WA->>R: WhatsApp notification

    alt Rider accepts
        R->>SYS: POST /api/rider/orders/[id]/accept
        SYS->>SYS: Assign rider, generate 6-digit pickup OTP
        SYS->>GW: POST /api/send-pickup-otp to vendor
        SYS->>GW: POST /api/send-rider-accepted to vendor
        GW->>WA: Vendor: Rider [Name] assigned. Pickup OTP: XXXXXX
        WA->>V: WhatsApp notification
        Note over V: OTP also shown on sales invoice
    else Rider rejects
        R->>SYS: POST /api/rider/orders/[id]/reject
        SYS->>LB: Try next available rider
        LB->>GW: Send assignment to next rider
    end

    Note over R,V: Rider arrives at vendor store

    V->>R: Tells rider the pickup OTP verbally (from invoice or WhatsApp)
    R->>SYS: POST /api/rider/orders/[id]/pickup { otp: XXXXXX }
    SYS->>SYS: Validate pickup_otp + expiry
    SYS->>SYS: Order → DISPATCHED, pickup_otp = null
    SYS->>SYS: Generate 6-digit delivery OTP
    SYS->>GW: POST /api/send-delivery-otp to customer
    GW->>WA: Customer: Rider is on the way. Delivery OTP: YYYYYY. Share with rider on arrival.
    WA->>C: WhatsApp notification

    Note over R,C: Rider arrives at customer address

    C->>R: Tells rider the delivery OTP verbally
    R->>SYS: POST /api/rider/orders/[id]/deliver { otp: YYYYYY }
    SYS->>SYS: Validate delivery_otp + expiry
    SYS->>SYS: Order → DELIVERED, delivery_otp = null
    SYS->>SYS: Clear rider assignment, mark rider available
    SYS->>GW: POST /api/send-payment-link to customer
    GW->>WA: Customer: Order delivered! Pay here: /pay/[id]?token=...
    WA->>C: WhatsApp payment link
